{"tid":648202,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"每日返工都好痛苦","createTime":"2018-04-30T13:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T00:33:54.000Z","uid":148,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6bc7cd9fe3018c9cd15bfebc70ae40d6b5e3e61","tid":648202,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"每次想做得好啲嘅時候就偏偏會出錯<br />\n諗起要返工就有種恐懼<br />\n踏入office 又要面對人事、工作上種種嘅壓力<br />\n唔識社交嘅毒撚 返工就要戴住假面具扮野迫自己social啲<br />\n但點扮都係扮唔到 融入唔到小圈子<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企又要面對屋企嘅壓力<br />\n然後每日就諗點樣行出呢個框框<br />\n又驚帶太多負能量返去<br />\n返工放工行屍走肉、無時無刻都好壓抑咁 如果唔是為錢為屋企人<br />\n應該會好撚自私咁完咗佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492d42d709f38b8a6619617b108cc3e2fa7f0fe1","tid":648202,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"已經無哂動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b55b6958a9ae8d8947553eea0cdb468f251a21","tid":648202,"uid":17781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"樓主番咪工呀？"},{"pid":"9fd417b662af73804e1eb8fac365fc8295e09820","tid":648202,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"492d42d709f38b8a6619617b108cc3e2fa7f0fe1","tid":648202,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"已經無哂動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8708d37b5cfeb1f72074b621c5d05fe92eede398","tid":648202,"uid":148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55b55b6958a9ae8d8947553eea0cdb468f251a21","tid":648202,"uid":17781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"樓主番咪工呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":