c9","tid":648202,"uid":51860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"我都知道返得工點都會被人鬧下<br />\n我阿頭都算好咖啦  只不過各種感覺好無助<br />\n努力做好但又不停做錯  最重要係唔拎到埋去都唔知道錯d乜<br />\nbtw多謝你啊巴打"},{"pid":"df68dcac2aa9bb1593ad7425b5db1ddbbc9b124e","tid":648202,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"fg 留名<br />\n以前summer係d 垃圾公司做過一陣<br />\n乜野training都無, d同事又中意卸膊<br />\n<br />\n樓主唔好灰心呀，工作真係好講緣分<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"cacaec4b03b895d8be40145ab52d39043d382a5f","tid":648202,"uid":17781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T20:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6441714be338db46bb51bf1108cd8474fc844624","tid":648202,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"好明白 岩岩出黎做野係咁"}]}